🧠 10. SECURITY CHECKLIST

Before deploying any AI model:

✔ Check organisation trust
✔ Check download volume
✔ Inspect file format
✔ Review security scan
✔ Read model card
✔ Compare with verified baseline
✔ Check community warnings

🛡️ 11. KEY TAKEAWAY

AI supply chains fail not because models are weak, but because:

Trust is assumed
Files are opaque
Dependencies are hidden
Updates are uncontrolled
🔥 FINAL PRINCIPLE

If you cannot verify every link in the AI supply chain, you cannot fully trust the model.
